if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('sys_adminpurview')
and type = 'U')
drop table sys_adminpurview
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sys_adminpurview */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sys_adminpurview (
AdminPurviewID int identity(1,1),
AdminID int not null default 0,
RoleID int not null default 0,
PurviewCode nvarchar(100) not null,
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
Isdel bit not null default 0,
constraint PK_SYS_ADMINPURVIEW primary key (AdminPurviewID)
)
go
